@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"] App Container</h1>

<div class="container text-start">

<h2 class="mt-5">To Do List</h2>

The to do list app is a simple and easy-to-use tool that helps you stay organized and on track. You can create lists for anything, from work to personal tasks, and set due dates and reminders. The app also includes a built-in timer and stopwatch, so you can track your progress and make sure you're staying on schedule.

<h2 class="mt-5">Random Quotes</h2>

The random quotes app is a fun and inspirational way to start your day. Each time you open the app, you'll be presented with a new quote from a famous person or author. You can also search for quotes by topic or keyword. The app is a great way to learn new things, boost your motivation, and add a little bit of wisdom to your day.

<h2 class="mt-5">BMI Calculator</h2>

The BMI calculator app is a quick and easy way to calculate your body mass index (BMI). BMI is a measure of body fat based on your height and weight. It's a useful tool for tracking your weight and health goals. The app also includes a BMI chart, so you can see how your BMI compares to others of your age and height.

<h2 class="mt-5">Weather Forecast</h2>

The weather forecast app is a handy tool for staying up-to-date on the latest weather conditions. The app provides current conditions, forecasts for the next few days, and a radar map. You can also set up alerts to be notified of weather changes. The app is a great way to plan your day and stay safe in bad weather.

<h2 class="mt-5">Conclusion</h2>

These are just a few of the many apps that are available to help you stay organized, motivated, and informed. With so many great options to choose from, you're sure to find the perfect app to help you achieve your goals.
</div>
